  {
    "page_no": 20,
    "block_id": "p20_b21",
    "block_type": "body",
    "source_text": "儘管2020年的新業務價值27.65億美元較2019年減少了33%，我們迅速採用了新的數碼工具，並且外出限制的普",
    "translation": "Although new business value of USD 2.765 billion in 2020 decreased 33% versus 2019, we rapidly adopted new digital tools, and relaxation of movement restrictions supported sales recovery.",
    "translation_source": "model_compact",
    "control_rule": "",
    "used_compact_retry": true,
    "fit_status_initial": "font_shrink",
    "fit_status_final": "font_shrink",
    "font_ratio_initial": 0.598,
    "font_ratio_final": 0.698,
    "font_size_final": 6.28,
    "layout_mode_initial": "single_line",
    "layout_mode_final": "single_line"
  },
  {
    "page_no": 20,
    "block_id": "p20_b22",
    "block_type": "body",
    "source_text": "遍放寬支持了銷售勢頭的恢復。友邦保險中國業務為2020年本集團的新業務價值帶來最大貢獻，也是我們第一個",
    "translation": "AIA's China business made the largest contribution to Group new business value in 2020 and was the first reporting segment to show sales recovery, as the region gradually relaxed strict lockdowns from March 2020.",
    "translation_source": "model_compact",
    "control_rule": "",
    "used_compact_retry": true,
    "fit_status_initial": "font_shrink",
    "fit_status_final": "font_shrink",
    "font_ratio_initial": 0.564,
    "font_ratio_final": 0.617,
    "font_size_final": 5.55,
    "layout_mode_initial": "single_line",
    "layout_mode_final": "single_line"
  },
  {
    "page_no": 20,
    "block_id": "p20_b23",
    "block_type": "body",
    "source_text": "顯示銷售勢頭有所恢復的報告分部，原因在於該地區自2020年3月逐步放寬嚴格的封鎖。撇除維持低位的中國內",
    "translation": "Excluding new business sales from Mainland China visitors to Hong Kong, which remained low, the Group's other segments showed strong recovery in new business value in H2, growing 23% versus H1.",
    "translation_source": "model_compact",
    "control_rule": "",
    "used_compact_retry": true,
    "fit_status_initial": "font_shrink",
    "fit_status_final": "font_shrink",
    "font_ratio_initial": 0.581,
    "font_ratio_final": 0.657,
    "font_size_final": 5.91,
    "layout_mode_initial": "single_line",
    "layout_mode_final": "single_line"
  },
  {
    "page_no": 20,
    "block_id": "p20_b24",
    "block_type": "body",
    "source_text": "地訪港旅客銷售額，本集團其他分部的新業務價值在下半年強勁復甦，與上半年相比增長了23%。本集團的新業",
    "translation": "The Group's new business momentum remained strong in 2021, with new business value in the first two months 15% higher than the corresponding 2020 period.",
    "translation_source": "model_compact",
    "control_rule": "",
    "used_compact_retry": true,
    "fit_status_initial": "font_shrink",
    "fit_status_final": "font_shrink",
    "font_ratio_initial": 0.785,
    "font_ratio_final": 0.836,
    "font_size_final": 7.52,
    "layout_mode_initial": "single_line",
    "layout_mode_final": "single_line"
  },
  {
    "page_no": 20,
    "block_id": "p20_b25",
    "block_type": "body",
    "source_text": "務發展勢頭在2021年持續強勁，首兩個月新業務價值較2020年同期高出15%。",
    "translation": "AIA's China business recorded strong momentum in 2021, with new business value in the first two months showing robust growth versus the corresponding 2020 period.",
    "translation_source": "model_compact",
    "control_rule": "",
    "used_compact_retry": true,
    "fit_status_initial": "font_shrink",
    "fit_status_final": "font_shrink",
    "font_ratio_initial": 0.518,
    "font_ratio_final": 0.571,
    "font_size_final": 5.14,
    "layout_mode_initial": "single_line",
    "layout_mode_final": "single_line"
  },
  {
    "page_no": 20,
    "block_id": "p20_b26",
    "block_type": "body",
    "source_text": "友邦保險中國業務在2021年錄得成功的勢頭，首兩個月的新業務價值與2020年同期比較，錄得非常強勁的增",
    "translation": "New business value of USD 968 million in 2020 decreased 17% versus 2019, primarily due to limited sales in Q1 following the initial COVID-19 outbreak.",
    "translation_source": "model_compact",
    "control_rule": "",
    "used_compact_retry": true,
    "fit_status_initial": "font_shrink",
    "fit_status_final": "ok",
    "font_ratio_initial": 0.76,
    "font_ratio_final": 0.882,
    "font_size_final": 7.94,
    "layout_mode_initial": "single_line",
    "layout_mode_final": "single_line"
  },
  {
    "page_no": 20,
    "block_id": "p20_b27",
    "block_type": "body",
    "source_text": "長。2020年新業務價值9.68億美元較2019年減少17%，主要由於2019冠狀病毒病在第一季爆發初期而導致銷售額",
    "translation": "As movement restrictions eased, new business momentum improved rapidly. New business value resumed customary seasonal patterns, with greater concentration in H1.",
    "translation_source": "model_compact",
    "control_rule": "",
    "used_compact_retry": true,
    "fit_status_initial": "font_shrink",
    "fit_status_final": "font_shrink",
    "font_ratio_initial": 0.664,
    "font_ratio_final": 0.815,
    "font_size_final": 7.34,
    "layout_mode_initial": "single_line",
    "layout_mode_final": "single_line"
  },
  {
    "page_no": 20,
    "block_id": "p20_b28",
    "block_type": "body",
    "source_text": "有限。隨著外出限制放寬，新業務動力得以迅速改善。新業務價值重拾我們慣常的季節性規律，比重更側重於上",
    "translation": "In 2020, AIA's China business made the largest contribution to the Group's new business value.",
    "translation_source": "model_initial",
    "control_rule": "",
    "used_compact_retry": false,
    "fit_status_initial": "ok",
    "fit_status_final": "ok",
    "font_ratio_initial": 1.0,
    "font_ratio_final": 1.0,
    "font_size_final": 9.0,
    "layout_mode_initial": "single_line",
    "layout_mode_final": "single_line"
  },
  {
    "page_no": 20,
    "block_id": "p20_b29",
    "block_type": "body",
    "source_text": "半年。在2020年，友邦保險中國業務為集團的新業務價值帶來最大貢獻。",
    "translation": "Following implementation of travel restrictions, new business sales from Mainland China visitors to AIA's Hong Kong business were effectively suspended from early February 2020, resulting in significant decline in new business value.",
    "translation_source": "model_compact",
    "control_rule": "",
    "used_compact_retry": true,
